column8: Must be senior 7A and above AND must have completed (SAFe Scrum Master OR SAFe Agilist Certification).Please nominate only if this certification is aligned towards Business or Organisational Requirement.

Title: Professional Scrum Master I Assessment
column8: Must be 7A and above.Practitioners must have IBM Agile explorer badge.Please do not nominate if practitioners are CSM  certified. This is a certification which does not have any mandated training. It is a Scrum.org certification. Practitioners if approved would be provided with cost of the certification.   Please nominate only if this certification is aligned towards Business or Organisational Requirement.

Title: Professional Scrum Master II Assessment
column8: Must be 7B and above. Practitioners must have the IBM Agile Advocate badge.Practitioners must be PSM1 certified.There is no mandated training associated with this certification.  Please nominate only if this certification is aligned towards Business or Organisational Requirement.

Please nominate only if this certification is aligned towards Business or Organisational Requirement.
